of literature when you read it at a
different time in your life it seems

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:46.920
completely new it always seems like a
wonder a mere court lady could have

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:52.320
written a thirteen hundred page book
with 54 chapters and some 500 characters

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:56.370
and one of the most remarkable things
about it is the way that it's written

00:00:56.370 --> 00:01:02.550
how it really it has this uncanny way of
feeling like a modern novel there are

