00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:48.360
Buddhist ceremony consecrating the space
because these aren't just artworks they

00:01:48.360 --> 00:01:53.369
are Buddhist sacred sculptures that have
a life of their own that need to be

00:01:53.369 --> 00:02:00.000
